Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.48,0:00:04.73,Copy of Main Dialog,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30}To Mr. Junichi Katsuragi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.48,0:00:04.73,Copy of Main Dialog,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30}I empathize with you. You were right about the way things are, \Nbut we should stand up for ourselves. And so, I have decided to form\N a publishing company together with a few of our comrades.\N I would like you to see it as the same battle but in a new \Nform, and I hope you will join me in this endeavor. I want to talk to \Nyou about this face to face.
