Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:46.46,Main Dialog,Maruo,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:47.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's next Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:49.25,Main Dialog,Girls A-B-C-D,0,0,0,,We'll be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:52.17,Main Dialog,Tokie,0,0,0,,Since Olympus is hosting it,\Nwill you play the guitar for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:55.42,Main Dialog,Maruo,0,0,0,,Well, if you've got a request...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:01:59.68,Main Dialog,Tokie,0,0,0,,Ri, are you going to the Christmas party too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:02.89,Main Dialog,Tokie,0,0,0,,You can go with Nishimi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:07.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm not really part of that group, so I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:11.94,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Sorry, my church is having a Christmas party on Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:13.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:16.11,Main Dialog,Maruo,0,0,0,,So Kawabuchi's going with you then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:16.57,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:19.24,Main Dialog,Maruo,0,0,0,,We should've checked before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:24.83,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Maruo, if you don't mind, I think I'd like to go to the party after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:25.70,Main Dialog,Maruo,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.91,Main Dialog,Maruo,0,0,0,,Of course, you're very welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:30.79,Main Dialog,Maruo,0,0,0,,{\a6}I never thought you'd agree to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:32.92,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's best to start putting a little distance between us like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:33.75,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:39.76,Main Dialog,Seiji,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:42.18,Main Dialog,Seiji,0,0,0,,You're late, Richie-baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:44.68,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,H-Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:47.48,Main Dialog,Seiji,0,0,0,,All right! Next we'll play The Spiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:48.77,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0,0,0,,What about The Beatles?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:51.19,Main Dialog,Seiji,0,0,0,,Let's go with "Bang Bang Bang"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:02.41,Main Dialog,Girl,0,0,0,,Nishimi, how about some cider?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:03.28,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:09.12,Main Dialog,Seiji,0,0,0,,Feigning innocence, bang bang bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.88,Main Dialog,Seiji,0,0,0,,Bang bang, bababababababa-bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:19.22,Main Dialog,Seiji,0,0,0,,He's someone I can't beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:24.35,Main Dialog,Seiji,0,0,0,,Bang bang, bababababababa-bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:27.56,Main Dialog,Girl,0,0,0,,Come on, Nishimi, let's sing together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:30.31,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I don't really know the popular songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:39.32,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I wonder what {\i1}he's{\i0}{\fscx125} {\r}doing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:43.32,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Maybe he's talking to Ri at the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:11.35,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I go to a party, and all I do is think about those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:13.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I feel like a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.23,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.15,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:20.44,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Why are you here? I thought\Nyou were going to church.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:25.66,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yeah. Their Christmas party is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:28.95,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,He isn't here with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.71,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Does he have to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:38.34,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Um... He took the munchkins home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:40.34,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:43.55,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's cold, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:44.38,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:47.60,Main Dialog,Sailor,0,0,0,,Hey, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:49.06,Main Dialog,Sailor,0,0,0,,I've got you, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:07.74,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, isn't his birthday coming up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:10.99,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I hope you finish in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:13.54,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:16.37,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Why do you say things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:18.00,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.29,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,This is for...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:23.38,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Never mind! You're an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:30.72,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What did I do this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:33.35,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:36.23,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Women are hard to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:42.23,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Why did I lose my temper like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:47.20,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm the one who rejected \Nhim in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:53.16,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Even if I finished knitting this,\NI'd never be able to give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:24.86,Main Dialog,Mom,0,0,0,,I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:29.91,Main Dialog,Mom,0,0,0,,You're safe for now, Yurika, \Nbut let me tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:30.99,Main Dialog,Yurika,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're going to tell me not to see him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:35.49,Main Dialog,Yurika,0,0,0,,You don't have to keep repeating yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:38.21,Main Dialog,Yurika,0,0,0,,Chet, get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:40.21,Main Dialog,Yurika,0,0,0,,Chet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:55.26,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Sentaro? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:58.48,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,What am I...? I've been waitin' for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:02.10,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Wh-Why are you acting so formal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:07.57,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Ri'ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:11.32,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:16.62,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I never realized how you felt till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:21.96,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I may have said some dumb things an' hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:26.46,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. But... Um... How should I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:30.76,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,About your feelings, I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:42.73,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Sentaro, why are you suddenly on your best behavior?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:44.73,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Stop it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:46.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This isn't a yakuza movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:48.99,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Did I get it wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:55.37,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yeah. You got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:00.08,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,O-Oh, a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:01.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry for talkin' so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:06.63,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Right! We're like family. You made \Nme nervous for a second there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:11.13,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I-In that case, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:19.14,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,We're like family, so I couldn't stand \Nthe thought of causin' you pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:28.15,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm glad I heard this now \Nand not a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:30.94,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:35.57,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm never going to tell a blockhead like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:48.67,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,There's something I have to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:52.42,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,I'm going back to Tokyo soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:59.10,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,You probably won't see me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:07.15,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,An upperclassman from my college is \Nstarting his own publishing company,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:09.07,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,and he wants me to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:12.53,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,I plan on leaving soon after New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:16.03,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,It's taken me a long time \Nto get to this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:19.03,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,but I owe it to you for making me think \NI should give going back one more try.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:20.66,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:25.41,Main Dialog,Yukari,0,0,0,,"Idiot. I don't want to hear those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:28.04,Main Dialog,Yukari,0,0,0,,Just don't leave me."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:31.96,Main Dialog,Yukari,0,0,0,,But I couldn't bring myself to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:35.55,Main Dialog,Yukari,0,0,0,,Not when he's finally trying to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.56,Main Dialog,Yurika,0,0,0,,Ritsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:44.23,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yurika!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:46.31,Main Dialog,Yurika,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:47.48,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Looking for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:51.23,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I carelessly threw something \Naway that was important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:53.61,Main Dialog,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey, is that girl homeless?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:55.95,Main Dialog,Yukari,0,0,0,,Hey, Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:58.57,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Never mind me. Please, go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:02.87,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,A beautiful girl like you shouldn't be seen doing something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:06.37,Main Dialog,Yukari,0,0,0,,Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:11.04,Main Dialog,Yukari,0,0,0,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:16.13,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,P-Please, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:17.42,Main Dialog,Yukari,0,0,0,,It's something important, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.43,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yurika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:23.60,Main Dialog,Yukari,0,0,0,,So, what am I looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:28.44,Main Dialog,Yukari,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:29.60,Main Dialog,Yukari,0,0,0,,This is it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:30.65,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:35.15,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,But I'll have to start over with clean yarn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:37.78,Main Dialog,Yukari,0,0,0,,Is this going to be a present for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:39.86,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:43.24,Main Dialog,Yukari,0,0,0,,Why did you throw away \Nsomething so important?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:50.50,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I was confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:57.38,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I suddenly felt stupid for knitting a \Ngift that I'd never be able to give.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:10:59.47,Main Dialog,Yukari,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't you be able to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:03.51,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,B-Because a lot of things \Nhave happened between us,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:06.43,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,and I hurt him terribly before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:07.27,Main Dialog,Yukari,0,0,0,,You turned him down, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:10.60,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,And I couldn't tell him I \Nlike him now after doing that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:12.27,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,so I decided to let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:15.61,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,But then I thought that wouldn't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:21.49,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,See, there was another time when \NI said nothing and just gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:24.33,Main Dialog,Yukari,0,0,0,,Do you regret it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:29.29,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,No. I'd given up on that long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:36.67,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Besides, I've realized this person has been there to support me all this time, whenever I've felt down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:42.43,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I had no confidence in myself,\Nbut he did his best to encourage me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:45.85,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,This time, I want to be the \None to tell him how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:51.19,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I finally decided to stop keeping my \Nmouth shut and waiting for things to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:58.69,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for talking about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:12:00.69,Main Dialog,Yukari,0,0,0,,No, I'm glad you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:03.70,Main Dialog,Yukari,0,0,0,,I think you've opened my eyes as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.45,Main Dialog,Yukari,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:08.37,Main Dialog,Yukari,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:10.00,Main Dialog,Yukari,0,0,0,,Who's your prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:11.91,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Oh, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:13.96,Main Dialog,Yukari,0,0,0,,Shall I try and guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:17.29,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you saying? Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:19.38,Main Dialog,Yukari,0,0,0,,You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:33.90,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm set to leave this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:38.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Working in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:42.37,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,Yeah. A lot happened at college,\Nand I ended up dropping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:48.46,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,But you'll come back once in a while, \Nwon't you? Like you've been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:51.59,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,No. I'm never coming back to this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:56.97,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,Kaoru, our sessions were fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.97,0:12:58.22,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,I'll miss seeing you and Sen-boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:13:01.80,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,but I don't want you guys \Nto stop playing jazz.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:05.93,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Jun! Haven't you told him you're going back to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:13.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey, Sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:17.11,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,What's the hubbub, Richie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:20.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's about Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.49,0:13:23.41,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's about to go back to Tokyo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.41,0:13:24.37,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I heard from Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:28.41,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Well, ain't got nothin' to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:31.38,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Now, wanna jam?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:33.13,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You're gonna let that be the last you see of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.38,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I got nothin' to say to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:41.01,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You've looked up to him like a\Nbig brother since you were a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.64,0:13:45.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You may never get the chance to see him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:47.10,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,There'd be no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:49.48,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Once he's gone, it'll be too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:53.61,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Enough about Jun already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:54.73,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Let's get started here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.79,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,If you don't feel like \Npracticin', I'm goin' home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:17.09,Main Dialog,Old Woman,0,0,0,,What's all the fuss about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:22.18,Main Dialog,Man,0,0,0,,I guess college students from Tokyo \Nand all over have come to demonstrate
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.18,0:14:24.34,Main Dialog,Man,0,0,0,,against letting the nuclear aircraft carrier into port.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.93,0:14:27.60,Main Dialog,Old Woman,0,0,0,,That's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:31.48,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,In their eyes, I'm a traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:35.48,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,They may never forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:37.57,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:44.07,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,all I can do is search in my own way from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:46.87,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,using a different method than them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:14:58.88,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Oh, you're here, Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:15:00.42,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Here, eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:02.88,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I made it myself, so it might be a little salty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:05.84,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,But if you're not gonna eat it, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:08.35,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Is this any time to be eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:10.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Did you forget what I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:14.98,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,What are you talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:16.31,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:18.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you going to be stubborn until it's too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:23.11,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,He's leaving either today or tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:24.20,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,It's tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:27.49,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,I'm taking the night train, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:34.29,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,Sen-boy, this was rather old-fashioned of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:36.29,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,I thought it was some kind of joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:38.13,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,It's no joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:41.55,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I wanted to have a serious showdown with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:47.05,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Wait, you're not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:49.30,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,I made it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:50.76,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,Let me in on it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.37,0:16:57.37,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,This is no duet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:17:02.13,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,They're seriously duking it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:29.32,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,Sorry for causing you so much trouble, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:33.16,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,Tell me about it! And when you reach Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:35.20,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,first thing you do is get to a barber!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:37.54,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:40.54,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,Well, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.38,0:17:44.50,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.84,0:17:50.72,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I'll remember today's session for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:57.35,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,Yeah. Me too, Sen-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:13.28,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:15.70,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I told you not to see me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:18.08,Main Dialog,Yurika,0,0,0,,I have four questions I want you to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:21.58,Main Dialog,Yurika,0,0,0,,If you try to dodge them, I'll \Nget on this train with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:24.46,Main Dialog,Yurika,0,0,0,,So answer me truthfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:29.92,Main Dialog,Yurika,0,0,0,,Question number one: Why did \Nyou tell me not to see you off?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:34.97,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,I hate sad goodbye scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.97,0:18:39.35,Main Dialog,Yurika,0,0,0,,Question number two: Did you ever consider taking me with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.27,0:18:43.52,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,The work I'm going to be doing is kind of a gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:46.90,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,Even if I took you with me, there's no \Nguarantee I'd make any kind of living.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:49.44,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,Besides, you're still in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:50.86,Main Dialog,Yurika,0,0,0,,Question number three...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:54.78,Main Dialog,Yurika,0,0,0,,Why didn't you do anything more than kiss me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:19:00.75,Main Dialog,Yurika,0,0,0,,Did you not touch me because you \Nintended to leave from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.00,0:19:04.75,Main Dialog,Yurika,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:09.88,Main Dialog,Yurika,0,0,0,,I knew. I knew how much you cared about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:14.51,Main Dialog,Yurika,0,0,0,,This is my last question:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.68,0:19:18.97,Main Dialog,Yurika,0,0,0,,Won't you take me with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:24.64,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,I want you to take good care of your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:35.91,Main Dialog,Yurika,0,0,0,,I figured you'd say something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:39.53,Main Dialog,Yurika,0,0,0,,Now I feel like I've been set free too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:43.54,Main Dialog,Yurika,0,0,0,,I'm going back to my own world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:46.54,Main Dialog,Yurika,0,0,0,,Thank you, Junichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:48.67,Main Dialog,Yurika,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.30,0:19:52.88,Main Dialog,Mom,0,0,0,,Yurika, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:54.55,Main Dialog,Mom,0,0,0,,Come out, Yurika!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:59.18,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,How dare you embarrass us by walking out in the middle of an arranged marriage meeting like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.18,0:20:00.56,Main Dialog,Mom,0,0,0,,Calm down, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:03.06,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,We're going back there together, Yurika!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.94,0:20:08.06,Main Dialog,Dad,0,0,0,,Yurika, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:18.41,Main Dialog,Yurika,0,0,0,,I'm going back to my own world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:42.26,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,I pulled you aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.39,0:20:44.60,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:47.85,Main Dialog,Yurika,0,0,0,,What is there to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:49.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The train's already left the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.65,0:20:50.77,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:56.03,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,Well, when we get there, we'll go to my room first,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.03,0:20:58.91,Main Dialog,Jun,0,0,0,,and maybe I'll have you cut my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.79,0:21:08.58,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's freezing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:11.59,Main Dialog,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah. Think I'll light the heater.
